title: Tudesco (Adenocarpus complicatus)
body: A shrubby legume with whitish branches, fasciculate and 3-foliate leaves, and yellow flowers, found on the Caminho do Meio and near the Choupana. Tudesco is a corruption of codesso.

Caminho do Meio: Where the shrubby legume is found
Choupana: Where the shrubby legume is found
